propel.core.utils
Class Linq

java.lang.Object
  propel.core.utils.Linq

public final class Linq
extends java.lang.Object

Provides similar functionality to .NET language integrated queries (LINQ). There are usually two versions of each function, one for operating on Iterables (such as collections) and one with arrays. This is because in Java, arrays are subclasses of Object and not of Iterable, Collection, List, etc.
